1. Moj pas je uhvatio *skota* u dvorištu. (My dog caught a *scoundrel* in the yard.)
2. Nikada ne bih želeo da budem *skot*. (I would never want to be a *jerk*.)
3. Znaš li ko je taj *skot* koji je pokušao da ukrade novac? (Do you know who that *bastard* was who tried to steal money?)
4. Na putu do kuće sreo sam nekoliko *skotova*. (On the way home, I met several *low-lifes*.)
5. Ne mogu da verujem da je toliko *skotova* na ovoj planeti. (I can't believe there are so many *scumbags* on this planet.)
6. Ovaj grad je pun *skotova* koji varaju turiste. (This city is full of *crooks* who scam tourists.)
7. Tvoj šef je pravi *skot* što te je tako loše tretirao. (Your boss is a real *jerk* for treating you so poorly.)
8. Moramo da se rešimo ovog *skota* iz komšiluka. (We need to get rid of this *jerk* from the neighborhood.)
9. Onaj *skot* se hvali svojim novcem, ali ga je nasledio od oca. (That *bastard* brags about his money, but he inherited it from his father.)
10. Nemoj da me tretiraš kao *skota* samo zato što se ne slažemo oko nečega. (Don't treat me like a *scoundrel* just because we don't agree on something.)